 />\n千石<br />\n🙂排名不分先後<br />\n<br />\n至於成日loop既歌就係化物語果首👍🏻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奏既面癱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑貓既中二<br />\n小野寺我都係超級鍾意 成日怕怕醜醜正到仆街<br />\n千石就公認...<br />\n<br />\n不過絕不能睇小絕園入面既不破愛花...配到個女神氣場勁到仆街..."},{"pid":"81b6f38d945b7c59059e21d4ff501cb0042f69ac","tid":383710,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢配貧窮神既櫻子真係估唔到<br />\n仲有幫電話賣廣告果到又係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想比佢鬧🤣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n櫻子成日要鬧窮神...好傷喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然近年香菜配既角色由腹黑到癲雞都有<br />\n但我最鍾意始終都係嘟嘟嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我鍾意幾個香菜配既角色<br />\n<br />\n立華奏<br />\n黑貓<br />\n小野寺<br />\n千石<br />\n🙂排名不分先後<br />\n<br />\n至於成日loop既歌就係化物語果首👍🏻</blockquote><br />\n胖虎版戀愛循環"},{"pid":"8f126b1faea5fd40c8d5ad5c28199bddcfd1ac7c","tid":383710,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"兵庫北"},{"pid":"f7c31f9b795a2d868aa97452d1311aec7c751a00","tid":383710,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:22:50.000Z","msg":"小野寺把聲好好j"},{"pid":"4246e10d92fffd080d280fcf52a093316aee2ea1","tid":383710,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好想笑"},{"pid":"78556d05461111d8337f1157234f53963182412b","tid":383710,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小野寺把聲好好j</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本香菜最適合呢類青春少女聲"},{"pid":"6af2d27f832f541cf76a202bf0150dc947fbbaf3","tid":383710,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj